textAnnotations.description:
DEMOCRATIC PAYBACK
FIRST WE WAIT FOR A TERRORIST
ATTACK. THEN WE EXPLOIT PEOPLE'S
CONFUSION AND GRIEF TO RAM
THROUGH OUR RADICAL
LEFT-WING AGENDA!
BIPARTISANSHIP IS CRAP! THE
LIBERAL BASE DEMANDS VENGEANCE.
WE'RE GONNA DO JUST WHAT BUSH DID
YOU GO
COMMISSAR
PELOS
WE'LL
RAISE
WAGES!
OF COURSE
THAT WOULD
BE WRONG
CLOSE THE
CONCENTRATION
CAMPS!
DOING RIGHT
ALWAYS IS
HEALTH
CARE!
STOP
TORTURING
I-13.0b
